node.text:
A day of in the life of nail polish💅 (not just the cake, me, I am nail polish)
Thank you guys for a wonderful @holotaco launch day and 4-hour long livestream🤓 So fun hanging out with chat for the pre-party, launch and after party🎉 and when the countdown clock broke💀 all LIVE😆 Stream is up on my second YouTube channel Simply Not Logical if you need some background entertainment this week!
💿The new @holotaco Remix collection is almost 90% sold out🥲 
➡️Collector’s box set and all polishes are limited edition for our 2nd anniversary🎉💜
🔴Going live again today at 5PM ET / 2PM PT for a 💅mixing stream! You tell me what colours to mix as a Bonus Track⚗️ see you there!
🙏Thank you everyone for your incredible support and excitement for the holo!! Orders starting to ship out s💿💿n
#holotaco #holotacoremix

node.text:
Thinking about sipping the H💿L💿 it’s so beautiful🥵🍹 do not drink the nail polish... paint it on your nails💅 NEW @holotaco PASTEL RAINBOW COLLECTION launched today❗️🤩 it’s what you’ve been asking for, what you’ve been DEMANDING MA’AM😆 pastel holos!!! In our best selling linear holographic formula💯 all 7 colours of the PASTEL RAINBOW💡🌈 in a giant pastel rainbow holo collector’s box✨ (box as always is limited edition and limited quantities, due to the time it takes to manufacture, the cost, and they also take up space in the holo warehouse😆) if you missed last years rainbow launch, DON’T MISS THIS ONE💡🌈💅
⚠️Box is over 50% sold out right now💀🥲⚠️
🎥Watch my reveal video on YouTube for a close-up of the holo✨ link in bio👆
#holotaco #pastelrainbow

node.text:
IT’S HERE🦄☁️💅✨😭
After months and months of me showing u basically the entire collection bc I am a product tester😂 Introducing the 🦄☁️Unicorn Dream🦄☁️ collection with sweet cotton-candy crèmes and magical Unicorn Skin iridescent flakie toppers🦄✨ Watch my YouTube video 👆link in bio👆 for the full reveal and demo! Did u see the new Unicorn Skins over black? Or white?😱 Shocking magic should be illegal⚠️
❗️➡️ Over 50% of collection box sets are gone now😅 As always our boxes are limited edition bc special materials✨ and we have limited quantities. If you want the whole set in the box, I suggest you grab yours soon before they go poof extinct like a unicorn🦄☁️
www.holotaco.com
@holotaco 
Thank you guys for all the love and excitement for this one!!! I hope your nails love it🦄💅
#unicornskin #unicorndream #holotaco
